snippet.title: Best VGM 1927 - Ecco : The Tides of Time (Sega CD) - Fin to Feather
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Sega CD
Ecco : The Tides of Time (1994)
Fin to Feather
Spencer Nilsen
